; height:1em; vertical-align:middle; fill:currentColor\">\n    <path d=\"m1807.093 1482.477 79.736 79.963-355.313 355.312H355.346L.035 1562.44l79.85-79.963 322.22 322.334H1484.76l322.334-322.334ZM997.677-.033v1167.02l355.313-355.313 79.962 79.85-491.858 491.633L449.46 891.524l79.962-79.85 355.313 355.313V-.033h112.941Z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><span class=\"screenreader-only\">Download investments-understanding-portfolio-risk-over-time-slide-deck.pptx</span></a></span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Data class: <span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\"><a class=\"inline_disabled preview_in_overlay\" title=\"data.xlsx\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/files/80824566?wrap=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-canvas-previewable=\"false\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/123249/files/80824566\" data-api-returntype=\"File\">data.xlsx</a><a class=\"file_download_btn\" role=\"button\" download=\"\" style=\"margin-inline-start: 5px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/files/80824566/download?download_frd=1\"><span role=\"presentation\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1920\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em; vertical-align:middle; fill:currentColor\">\n    <path d=\"m1807.093 1482.477 79.736 79.963-355.313 355.312H355.346L.035 1562.44l79.85-79.963 322.22 322.334H1484.76l322.334-322.334ZM997.677-.033v1167.02l355.313-355.313 79.962 79.85-491.858 491.633L449.46 891.524l79.962-79.85 355.313 355.313V-.033h112.941Z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><span class=\"screenreader-only\">Download data.xlsx</span></a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\">Assignments and Quizzes</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><a title=\"PQ1\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/quizzes/503735\" data-course-type=\"quizzes\" data-published=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/123249/quizzes/503735\" data-api-returntype=\"Quiz\">PQ1</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Q1\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/quizzes/504286\" data-course-type=\"quizzes\" data-published=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/123249/quizzes/504286\" data-api-returntype=\"Quiz\">Q1</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Additional Resources</strong></span></p>\n<p>Chapter 5<a class=\"inline_disabled external\" href=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span></span><span class=\"external_link_icon\" style=\"margin-inline-start: 5px; display: inline-block; text-indent: initial; \" role=\"presentation\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1920\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em; vertical-align:middle; fill:currentColor\">\n    <path d=\"M1226.667 267c88.213 0 160 71.787 160 160v426.667H1280v-160H106.667v800C106.667 1523 130.56 1547 160 1547h1066.667c29.44 0 53.333-24 53.333-53.333v-213.334h106.667v213.334c0 88.213-71.787 160-160 160H160c-88.213 0-160-71.787-160-160V427c0-88.213 71.787-160 160-160Zm357.706 442.293 320 320c20.8 20.8 20.8 54.614 0 75.414l-320 320-75.413-75.414 228.907-228.906H906.613V1013.72h831.254L1508.96 784.707l75.413-75.414Zm-357.706-335.626H160c-29.44 0-53.333 24-53.333 53.333v160H1280V427c0-29.333-23.893-53.333-53.333-53.333Z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path>\n</svg>\n<span class=\"screenreader-only\">Links to an external site.</span></span></a></p>\n<p>Merrill Lynch maintenance margin calculation: <a class=\"inline_disabled external\" href=\"https://www.merrilledge.com/trade/margin-maintenance-call\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span>https://www.merrilledge.com/trade/margin-maintenance-call</span><span class=\"external_link_icon\" style=\"margin-inlin