	"contentText": "Week 6\n  \n  \n  \n    Overview\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nInterest rates and inflation (determining factors, nominal vs real interest rates, Fischer effect), historical returns (return calculation, historical distribution of returns), return statistics (mean return and return volatility, normal distributions vs fat tails, probability distributions), downside risk, returns of long-term investments (long-run vs short-run returns, compounding effects, lognormal distributions)\n\n\n\n\n \n\n\n\n\n \nLearning Objectives\nUpon completion of this week, you will be able to understand:\n\nthe difference between nominal vs real interest rates\nthe determinant factors of interest rates and inflation\nhow to calculate returns\nhow to build historical distributions of returns and calculate basic statistics from them\ndifferent types of return distributions commonly encountered in financial markets\nextreme events, distributions with fat tails, and downside risk\ndistinction between historical vs probability distribution\nshort-run vs long-run returns\n\n \nPreparation for class\nMandatory reading:\nLecture 3: lecture 3.pdf\n    \n\nDownload lecture 3.pdf\nLecture 3 supplement (FRB's Monetary policy in detail): lecture 3 sup.pdf\n    \n\nDownload lecture 3 sup.pdf\n \nClass\nClass zoom link: Class logistics \n \nData work\n\nUnderstanding portfolio risk over time:\n\nWRDS Introduction: investments-understanding-portfolio-risk-over-time-slide-deck.pptx\n    \n\nDownload investments-understanding-portfolio-risk-over-time-slide-deck.pptx\n\n\nData class: data.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload data.xlsx\n\n \nAssignments and Quizzes\nPQ1\nQ1\n \nAdditional Resources\nChapter 5\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nMerrill Lynch maintenance margin calculation: https://www.merrilledge.com/trade/margin-maintenance-call\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nMerrill Lynch margin calls: https://www.merrilledge.com/trade/margin-calls\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nFederal Reserve Banks' monetary policy: https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy.htm\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nHistorical Federal Funds Rate: https://www.federalreserve.gov/economy-at-a-glance-policy-rate.htm\n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\n \n \nClass Notes\nSep 23 class recording:\nhttps://cuboulder.zoom.us/rec/share/a6m7Vd4SlCiMYB3GRj4i9VgF3PwaLJLJHs0oLF8PUDAKp_EiM4W7QwiZOMie7qkO.3BPrOK1DXR4e3CO2 \n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nPasscode: Sn@W+DM1\nClass notes: Fnce3030 Sep 23.pdf\n    \n\nDownload Fnce3030 Sep 23.pdf\n \nSep 25 class recording: \nhttps://cuboulder.zoom.us/rec/share/4FkbnjcFb4izywJkVBY1aEaS7u-zBQlJBwW6zovzbk8RWPY6-BmYUDecXE7vV0uS.EJc7-NT8i27Otqne \n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nPasscode: 1&d!$a.u\nClass notes: data_work.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload data_work.xlsx\n  \n  \n\n",
